WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:07.868 --> 00:01:11.872 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:01:11.955 --> 00:01:13.290 line:20%
64TH ARCHERY EXHIBITION MATCH

00:01:13.373 --> 00:01:15.625 line:20%
[scorekeeper] Hyeonmu House,
Black Tortoise of the North!

00:01:15.709 --> 00:01:17.168 line:80%
[cheering]

00:01:17.252 --> 00:01:19.754 line:80%
Cheongnyong House,
Azure Dragon of the East!

00:01:19.838 --> 00:01:21.256 line:80%
[cheering]

00:01:26.136 --> 00:01:28.138 line:80%
Jujak House, Vermilion Bird of the South!

00:01:28.221 --> 00:01:30.348 line:80%
[cheering]

00:01:35.687 --> 00:01:37.772 line:80%
Baekho House, White Tiger of the West!

00:01:38.690 --> 00:01:40.025 line:80%
That brat is Jujak's rep?

00:01:41.192 --> 00:01:42.903 line:80%
She's pretty good. I saw her practice.

00:01:43.612 --> 00:01:46.364 line:80%
I got this key from Ryu Minseok,
Cheongnyong House, ninth grade.

00:01:47.407 --> 00:01:49.075 line:80%
[Minseok] She is one vicious brat.

00:01:49.159 --> 00:01:51.912 line:80%
Just last month,
she couldn't even break a seven.

00:01:52.704 --> 00:01:54.706 line:80%
Why are you always so hostile toward her?

00:01:54.789 --> 00:01:56.124 line:80%
Do you like her?

00:01:56.750 --> 00:01:59.127 line:80%
[scoffs] A lowly creature like her?

00:02:00.211 --> 00:02:01.838 line:80%
-Are you insane?
-[I-AN] Ryu Minseok.

00:02:01.922 --> 00:02:03.214 line:80%
Yes?

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:05.008 line:80%
Watch your mouth.

00:02:05.926 --> 00:02:07.844 line:80%
-Pardon?
-Your vulgarity…

00:02:09.638 --> 00:02:11.222 line:80%
offends my eyes and ears.

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:16.061 line:80%
Understood.

00:02:21.524 --> 00:02:23.652 line:80%
[cheering]

00:02:23.735 --> 00:02:26.321 line:80%
[audience members]
Let's go, Cheongnyong House!

00:02:26.404 --> 00:02:28.156 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.033 line:80%
Good luck!

00:02:40.543 --> 00:02:42.295 line:80%
Ten points!

00:02:47.968 --> 00:02:49.386 line:80%
Nine points!

00:02:50.053 --> 00:02:51.513 line:80%
[screams]

00:02:51.596 --> 00:02:53.640 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:02:54.599 --> 00:02:55.642 line:80%
My goodness.

00:02:55.725 --> 00:02:58.395 line:80%
The students' enthusiasm
is truly remarkable, isn't it?

00:02:58.979 --> 00:03:02.065 line:80%
News of Your Majesty's attendance
really fired them up. [chuckles]

00:03:02.732 --> 00:03:03.942 line:80%
Word has reached me

00:03:04.609 --> 00:03:06.528 line:80%
that the archery range was open
around the clock.

00:03:06.611 --> 00:03:08.071 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:03:08.655 --> 00:03:11.491 line:80%
It was a personal request
from Grand Prince I-AN.

00:03:13.076 --> 00:03:15.662 line:80%
-[drum booming]
-[cheering]

00:03:24.254 --> 00:03:26.798 line:80%
[audience members]
Cheongnyong House, you're so cool!

00:03:26.881 --> 00:03:29.092 line:80%
-Go, Cheongnyong House!
-Cheongnyong!

00:03:29.175 --> 00:03:32.804 line:80%
-Cheongnyong of the East!
-Cheongnyong of the East!

00:03:33.763 --> 00:03:35.765 line:80%
[♪ determined music plays]

00:03:50.321 --> 00:03:51.823 line:80%
[scorekeeper] Nine points!

00:03:51.906 --> 00:03:54.075 line:80%
[cheering]

00:04:05.003 --> 00:04:06.004 line:80%
Come on…

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:12.052 line:80%
[scorekeeper] Ten points!

00:04:13.094 --> 00:04:14.095 line:80%
[sighs]

00:04:19.893 --> 00:04:22.562 line:80%
[cheering]

00:04:23.980 --> 00:04:25.982 line:80%
It's okay. We still have one more round.

00:04:26.941 --> 00:04:28.276 line:80%
We can turn it around then.

00:04:39.871 --> 00:04:41.790 line:80%
HYEONMU, CHEONGNYONG,
JUJAK, BAEKHO

00:04:42.624 --> 00:04:45.335 line:80%
It appears victory belongs to
House Cheongnyong this year.

00:04:46.044 --> 00:04:47.337 line:80%
I am not so sure.

00:04:47.420 --> 00:04:48.713 line:80%
It is not over

00:04:49.756 --> 00:04:51.091 line:80%
until it is truly over.

00:04:53.676 --> 00:04:55.512 line:80%
[scorekeeper] Last round!

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:58.431 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:05:00.225 --> 00:05:01.810 line:80%
[audience member] You got this!

00:05:01.893 --> 00:05:04.312 line:80%
-Go, Cheongnyong!
-Go, Jujak!

00:05:04.395 --> 00:05:05.563 line:80%
You got this, Jujak!

00:05:06.189 --> 00:05:07.482 line:80%
[cheering]

00:05:13.822 --> 00:05:15.323 line:80%
[audio fades]

00:05:15.406 --> 00:05:18.368 line:80%
[♪ determined music plays]

00:05:39.264 --> 00:05:40.723 line:80%
[scorekeeper] Nine points!

00:05:40.807 --> 00:05:42.642 line:80%
JUJAK: 110 POINTS

00:05:58.032 --> 00:05:59.868 line:80%
-[arrow thuds]
-[cheering]

00:06:10.295 --> 00:06:12.088 line:20%
EPISODE 2

00:06:15.008 --> 00:06:16.176 line:80%
Let's…

00:06:17.385 --> 00:06:18.386 line:80%
get married.

00:06:20.805 --> 00:06:22.098 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:06:51.461 --> 00:06:52.670 line:20%
What are the terms?

00:06:53.588 --> 00:06:54.756 line:20%
You don't seem surprised.

00:06:54.839 --> 00:06:56.049 line:20%
[chuckles]

00:06:56.132 --> 00:06:57.133 line:20%
Why should I be?

00:06:57.217 --> 00:06:59.886 line:20%
-There must've been plenty before me.
-There have.

00:06:59.969 --> 00:07:03.306 line:20%
Just in the past two days,
I've received dozens of match proposals.

00:07:10.230 --> 00:07:11.522 line:80%
[sighs] Damn it.

00:07:15.818 --> 00:07:16.903 line:80%
So…

00:07:18.738 --> 00:07:19.864 line:80%
state your terms.

00:07:24.244 --> 00:07:26.496 line:80%
I shall personally assess them.

00:07:28.998 --> 00:07:29.999 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:07:33.253 --> 00:07:34.420 line:80%
[clears throat, sighs]

00:07:36.631 --> 00:07:37.715 line:80%
I have a lot of money.

00:07:39.968 --> 00:07:40.969 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:07:42.387 --> 00:07:44.681 line:80%
[laughing]

00:07:48.393 --> 00:07:50.812 line:80%
I was expecting something
a little more creative.

00:07:50.895 --> 00:07:52.814 line:80%
No point in wasting creativity.

00:07:52.897 --> 00:07:54.941 line:80%
Arranged marriages are all the same.

00:07:56.567 --> 00:07:57.568 line:80%
After all,

00:07:59.362 --> 00:08:01.531 line:80%
familiarity makes everything feel better,

00:08:02.115 --> 00:08:04.575 line:80%
from the food you eat,
to the path you take,

00:08:05.326 --> 00:08:06.619 line:80%
even the clothes you wear.

00:08:07.829 --> 00:08:09.747 line:80%
That's why you reach for them.

00:08:10.832 --> 00:08:12.333 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:08:13.084 --> 00:08:14.085 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:08:16.254 --> 00:08:17.255 line:80%
So?

00:08:17.964 --> 00:08:19.424 line:80%
An assessment of the familiarity.

00:08:20.216 --> 00:08:22.677 line:80%
My pedigree is impressive,
and my acumen sharper still.

00:08:23.177 --> 00:08:24.679 line:80%
I have an older brother,

00:08:25.388 --> 00:08:26.639 line:80%
but you don't need to worry.

00:08:26.723 --> 00:08:29.809 line:80%
He's too dumb to cause any trouble.

00:08:32.895 --> 00:08:35.273 line:80%
I know you don't like it
when in-laws overstep.

00:08:37.025 --> 00:08:38.026 line:80%
What else?

00:08:40.486 --> 00:08:41.696 line:80%
[sighs]

00:08:42.363 --> 00:08:43.531 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:08:44.824 --> 00:08:45.867 line:80%
[inhales sharply]

00:08:45.950 --> 00:08:47.076 line:80%
I've got thick skin.

00:08:48.369 --> 00:08:51.414 line:80%
A successful woman and the bastard heir
to a conglomerate empire.

00:08:52.707 --> 00:08:55.501 line:80%
Do you have any idea
how much criticism I face every day?

00:08:55.585 --> 00:08:58.921 line:80%
Your Royal Highness
would never know in a million years.

00:08:59.005 --> 00:09:00.381 line:80%
It's better that way.

00:09:01.632 --> 00:09:03.885 line:80%
And I will make sure you never find out.

00:09:05.094 --> 00:09:06.179 line:80%
So just use me

00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.431 line:80%
as your human shield.

00:09:11.142 --> 00:09:13.227 line:20%
Pew…

00:09:13.311 --> 00:09:14.479 line:20%
-[clicks tongue]
-[grunts]

00:09:15.229 --> 00:09:16.731 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:09:18.399 --> 00:09:21.194 line:80%
We're getting divorced
once the contract is over anyway.

00:09:22.153 --> 00:09:23.529 line:80%
And even then,

00:09:24.947 --> 00:09:25.948 line:80%
I'll take the hit.

00:09:27.408 --> 00:09:28.409 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:09:32.288 --> 00:09:33.414 line:80%
Anything else?

00:09:37.668 --> 00:09:38.669 line:80%
Beauty?

00:09:38.753 --> 00:09:39.754 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:09:40.671 --> 00:09:41.672 line:80%
What else?

00:09:42.590 --> 00:09:44.884 line:80%
-You need more?
-Yeah. What else?

00:09:46.094 --> 00:09:47.095 line:80%
[sighs]

00:09:50.014 --> 00:09:51.057 line:80%
[grunts]

00:09:55.186 --> 00:09:56.354 line:80%
-Areum?
-[gasps]

00:09:57.814 --> 00:09:59.941 line:80%
-Aide Choi.
-What are you doing here?

00:10:00.566 --> 00:10:03.403 line:80%
Well, it's time for his herbal tonic.

00:10:03.486 --> 00:10:04.695 line:80%
[gasps]

00:10:04.779 --> 00:10:05.822 line:80%
Such perfect timing.

00:10:05.905 --> 00:10:07.824 line:80%
I can bring it to him. Give it to me.

00:10:08.533 --> 00:10:09.700 line:80%
Ah…

00:10:11.744 --> 00:10:13.454 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, it is Hyeon.

00:10:20.169 --> 00:10:21.379 line:80%
[sighs]

00:10:26.717 --> 00:10:28.261 line:80%
I-I have your tonic--

00:10:28.344 --> 00:10:30.012 line:80%
-Leave it there and go.
-Yes, sir.

00:10:31.097 --> 00:10:33.099 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

00:10:35.017 --> 00:10:37.437 line:80%
[door opens, closes]

00:10:55.997 --> 00:10:57.373 line:80%
[court lady] <i>Your Majesty.</i>

00:10:57.457 --> 00:11:00.001 line:80%
Jaegyeong of the Kim Family has arrived.

00:11:03.504 --> 00:11:04.505 line:80%
Show her in.

00:11:25.485 --> 00:11:29.155 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:11:29.238 --> 00:11:30.948 line:80%
CASTLE BEAUTY

00:11:31.574 --> 00:11:33.326 line:80%
-Has Ms. Seong come in yet?
-What?

00:11:33.409 --> 00:11:34.577 line:80%
Yes, she just came in.

00:11:36.037 --> 00:11:37.455 line:80%
[humming]

00:11:40.541 --> 00:11:41.542 line:80%
[knocks on door]

00:11:42.793 --> 00:11:43.961 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:11:45.213 --> 00:11:47.840 line:80%
What is it? Why are you smiling?

00:11:48.799 --> 00:11:50.551 line:80%
You don't even like me smiling now?

00:11:51.260 --> 00:11:53.262 line:80%
You shouldn't be smiling right now.

00:11:53.346 --> 00:11:55.848 line:80%
Have you lost your mind?
Or are you being punished?

00:11:56.474 --> 00:11:57.475 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-[gasps]

00:11:58.434 --> 00:12:00.811 line:80%
Is he going to force you to drink poison?

00:12:00.895 --> 00:12:02.104 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:12:02.188 --> 00:12:03.397 line:80%
Don't be ridiculous.

00:12:03.481 --> 00:12:04.899 line:80%
This isn't the Joseon Dynasty.

00:12:05.399 --> 00:12:06.692 line:80%
Ah…

00:12:06.776 --> 00:12:07.777 line:80%
Exactly.

00:12:08.361 --> 00:12:10.696 line:80%
So what happened? Update me already.

00:12:11.280 --> 00:12:12.323 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:13.991 --> 00:12:14.992 line:80%
I was rejected.

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:17.203 line:80%
What?

00:12:19.622 --> 00:12:20.748 line:80%
I said I was rejected.

00:12:21.791 --> 00:12:22.833 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>I decline.</i>

00:12:24.293 --> 00:12:26.254 line:80%
-May I ask why?
-Because there is…

00:12:27.588 --> 00:12:30.967 line:80%
[sighs] …something I value more
than wealth, ability, and beauty.

00:12:31.050 --> 00:12:32.426 line:80%
And what might that be?

00:12:32.510 --> 00:12:33.511 line:80%
If I tell you,

00:12:35.263 --> 00:12:36.347 line:80%
can you give it to me?

00:12:36.430 --> 00:12:37.640 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:12:38.516 --> 00:12:39.684 line:80%
You think I can't?

00:12:41.978 --> 00:12:42.979 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:12:43.062 --> 00:12:45.314 line:80%
So? What did he say he needs?

00:12:47.358 --> 00:12:48.484 line:80%
Love.

00:12:49.402 --> 00:12:50.403 line:80%
Huh?

00:12:50.486 --> 00:12:52.071 line:80%
He wishes to marry for love.

00:12:52.947 --> 00:12:54.156 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:56.576 line:80%
It's been his lifelong dream, apparently.

00:12:57.618 --> 00:12:59.328 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[mutters]

00:12:59.412 --> 00:13:01.497 line:80%
He's more of a romantic than you'd think.

00:13:02.164 --> 00:13:04.417 line:80%
-Romantic, my foot.
-You scared me.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:06.294 line:80%
He's clearly just screwing with me.

00:13:07.420 --> 00:13:09.171 line:80%
[Hyeon] So you screwed her over.

00:13:10.006 --> 00:13:12.008 line:80%
I thought you two went to the same school.

00:13:12.550 --> 00:13:15.845 line:80%
You could've just said no
and politely declined her offer.

00:13:15.928 --> 00:13:17.138 line:80%
You should've been nicer.

00:13:17.221 --> 00:13:18.347 line:80%
You can be so mean.

00:13:20.933 --> 00:13:21.934 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:13:22.018 --> 00:13:24.020 line:80%
[Ms. Do] <i>I'll look for another candidate.</i>

00:13:24.645 --> 00:13:25.646 line:80%
Why?

00:13:26.897 --> 00:13:28.733 line:80%
Since you were rejected.

00:13:28.816 --> 00:13:30.109 line:80%
So?

00:13:30.192 --> 00:13:32.987 line:80%
What? Are you going to try again?

00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:34.196 line:80%
Yeah.

00:13:34.697 --> 00:13:36.741 line:80%
Why? You weren't even sincere about it.

00:13:36.824 --> 00:13:39.160 line:80%
Oh, please. I couldn't be more sincere.

00:13:39.243 --> 00:13:40.328 line:80%
As if.

00:13:40.411 --> 00:13:41.912 line:80%
What kind of "sincere" person

00:13:41.996 --> 00:13:44.832 line:80%
would say, "I've got money, power,
a deadbeat brother,

00:13:44.915 --> 00:13:47.335 line:80%
and I'll even sign the divorce papers"?

00:13:47.418 --> 00:13:49.086 line:80%
Not a shred of modesty to be found.

00:13:49.587 --> 00:13:50.588 line:80%
Ms. Do.

00:13:51.547 --> 00:13:56.469 line:80%
Prince I-AN is already surrounded
by a horde armed with calculated modesty.

00:13:56.552 --> 00:13:59.555 line:80%
What do you think it'll take
to win against them?

00:14:01.265 --> 00:14:03.934 line:80%
You need a strategy to set yourself apart.

00:14:04.518 --> 00:14:05.561 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:14:05.645 --> 00:14:06.646 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:14:07.355 --> 00:14:10.775 line:80%
So are you saying
you intentionally pulled that crazy stunt?

00:14:10.858 --> 00:14:14.528 line:80%
I'm sure he's fond of eccentrics like me.

00:14:14.612 --> 00:14:16.656 line:80%
Birds of a feather flock together.

00:14:17.990 --> 00:14:21.869 line:80%
He showed up to His Majesty's
Royal Birthday Banquet in a <i>cheollik.</i>

00:14:21.952 --> 00:14:23.788 line:80%
That's not "normal," is it?

00:14:25.206 --> 00:14:28.501 line:80%
Were you not set
on Jaegyeong of the Kim Family?

00:14:28.584 --> 00:14:29.710 line:80%
PROSPECTIVE CONSORT

00:14:29.794 --> 00:14:31.337 line:80%
I do not intend to play matchmaker.

00:14:33.589 --> 00:14:35.174 line:80%
I would rather remain a spectator.

00:14:38.260 --> 00:14:42.890 line:80%
The more people interfere,
the greater the conflict grows.

00:14:43.474 --> 00:14:44.475 line:80%
In the end,

00:14:45.643 --> 00:14:48.020 line:80%
the one who staged it
will emerge the winner.

00:14:48.104 --> 00:14:49.438 line:80%
Does that mean…

00:14:54.110 --> 00:14:55.778 line:80%
I must meet this maiden.

00:14:59.115 --> 00:15:01.117 line:80%
[♪ imposing music plays]

00:15:08.082 --> 00:15:09.291 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:15:12.253 --> 00:15:14.422 line:80%
You said to prepare the new proposal
by next week--

00:15:14.505 --> 00:15:16.215 line:80%
-Listen…
-I'll have it by this evening.

00:15:16.799 --> 00:15:18.050 line:80%
Mm-mmm.

00:15:18.801 --> 00:15:21.220 line:80%
You can give that to me next week.

00:15:21.303 --> 00:15:22.304 line:80%
Pardon?

00:15:23.097 --> 00:15:24.098 line:80%
Then why…

00:15:24.849 --> 00:15:26.350 line:80%
You do know…

00:15:27.184 --> 00:15:29.353 line:80%
how much I rely on you,

00:15:30.438 --> 00:15:32.356 line:80%
don't you? [giggles]

00:15:33.065 --> 00:15:35.317 line:80%
[chuckles] M-Me? Y-You rely on me?

00:15:36.610 --> 00:15:37.611 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:15:38.863 --> 00:15:40.698 line:80%
I am aware.

00:15:40.781 --> 00:15:43.033 line:80%
With that in mind,

00:15:43.951 --> 00:15:46.829 line:80%
may I ask a small, secret favor

00:15:47.413 --> 00:15:48.789 line:80%
of you?

00:15:48.873 --> 00:15:51.333 line:80%
A secret favor?

00:15:51.417 --> 00:15:52.835 line:80%
Secret.

00:15:53.586 --> 00:15:54.587 line:80%
[giggles]

00:16:03.179 --> 00:16:04.597 line:80%
W-W-Why? What's wrong?

00:16:04.680 --> 00:16:07.308 line:80%
You're so out of it.
What are you even looking at?

00:16:08.184 --> 00:16:09.977 line:80%
What did she say?

00:16:11.187 --> 00:16:13.439 line:80%
-She's getting married.
-Huh?

00:16:13.522 --> 00:16:14.565 line:80%
[gasps]

00:16:14.648 --> 00:16:15.941 line:80%
[inhales sharply]

00:16:20.529 --> 00:16:23.199 line:80%
Right… Wait, she's getting married?

00:16:23.282 --> 00:16:24.325 line:80%
Mom.

00:16:24.867 --> 00:16:27.828 line:80%
You know that uncle
you mentioned last time?

00:16:27.912 --> 00:16:28.996 line:80%
Yeah.

00:16:29.079 --> 00:16:31.207 line:80%
Not the one who went to jail.
I don't like him!

00:16:32.249 --> 00:16:33.501 line:80%
[passerby clears throat]

00:16:35.085 --> 00:16:37.379 line:80%
The one who works
at the Royal Secretariat.

00:16:37.463 --> 00:16:38.506 line:80%
Yes, that's right.

00:16:39.006 --> 00:16:41.550 line:80%
Do you think I could get
his contact information?

00:16:42.134 --> 00:16:43.761 line:80%
[line ringing]

00:16:43.844 --> 00:16:45.095 line:80%
Goodness, Reporter Park.

00:16:45.179 --> 00:16:46.889 line:80%
It's me. Have you been well?

00:16:46.972 --> 00:16:47.973 line:80%
Yes, of course.

00:16:48.933 --> 00:16:50.935 line:80%
No, Ms. Seong is doing very well.

00:16:51.018 --> 00:16:52.186 line:80%
Yes, that's right.

00:16:52.770 --> 00:16:56.148 line:80%
So, Reporter Kim,
I heard you are a royal correspondent.

00:16:56.232 --> 00:16:57.775 line:80%
Ah, in that case,

00:16:58.400 --> 00:17:01.737 line:80%
you must have connections
with the Public Affairs Office as well.

00:17:01.821 --> 00:17:03.155 line:80%
Ah…

00:17:03.239 --> 00:17:04.907 line:80%
Yes, that's right. [chuckles]

00:17:06.116 --> 00:17:08.828 line:80%
[inhales sharply]
He's taking some time off,

00:17:08.911 --> 00:17:10.412 line:80%
so no official engagements.

00:17:10.496 --> 00:17:13.457 line:80%
The Royal Guard
accompanies him for all that,

00:17:13.541 --> 00:17:16.710 line:80%
-so he'd be impossible to approach.
-Is that so?

00:17:17.211 --> 00:17:18.295 line:80%
However,

00:17:18.963 --> 00:17:21.549 line:80%
he's bound to have informal engagements.

00:17:21.632 --> 00:17:24.760 line:80%
As it turns out, there are a few spots
he visits frequently.

00:17:24.844 --> 00:17:27.179 line:80%
-[laughs]
-[chuckles]

00:17:33.394 --> 00:17:35.187 line:80%
I've managed to compile

00:17:36.564 --> 00:17:37.690 line:80%
a comprehensive list.

00:17:38.315 --> 00:17:39.441 line:80%
[sighs]

00:17:41.235 --> 00:17:43.445 line:80%
-Thank you. I'll let you get back to work.
-[chuckles]

00:17:44.446 --> 00:17:45.823 line:80%
W-Wait, Ms. Do.

00:17:48.826 --> 00:17:49.952 line:80%
[mutters, sighs]

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:53.831 line:80%
Am I part of Ms. Seong's circle now?

00:17:53.914 --> 00:17:54.999 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:17:56.542 --> 00:17:58.168 line:80%
Of course.

00:17:58.252 --> 00:17:59.420 line:80%
Without a doubt.

00:18:01.589 --> 00:18:02.673 line:80%
Ah…

00:18:07.136 --> 00:18:08.846 line:80%
[gasps, sighs]

00:18:11.223 --> 00:18:13.559 line:80%
[horse whinnies]

00:18:13.642 --> 00:18:15.644 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:18:23.611 --> 00:18:24.612 line:80%
Hyah!

00:18:26.280 --> 00:18:27.698 line:80%
[horse whinnies]

00:18:33.329 --> 00:18:34.830 line:80%
-Whoa, whoa…
-[horse whinnies]

00:18:35.915 --> 00:18:36.916 line:80%
[sighs]

00:18:41.086 --> 00:18:42.588 line:80%
[sighs]

00:18:46.425 --> 00:18:48.552 line:80%
-[horse whinnies]
-Hmm?

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:53.182 line:80%
[♪ upbeat pop music plays]

00:18:53.265 --> 00:18:54.600 line:80%
Hyah!

00:18:54.683 --> 00:18:55.684 line:80%
Hyah!

00:18:57.353 --> 00:18:58.479 line:80%
Seong Huiju?

00:19:01.523 --> 00:19:02.650 line:80%
[Huiju] Hyah!

00:19:06.445 --> 00:19:07.655 line:80%
Whoa…

00:19:09.198 --> 00:19:10.199 line:80%
[sighs]

00:19:10.991 --> 00:19:12.993 line:80%
It's been a while, Your Royal Highness.

00:19:14.119 --> 00:19:15.579 line:80%
I believe it has been two days.

00:19:15.663 --> 00:19:16.705 line:80%
Isn't it odd?

00:19:17.206 --> 00:19:19.541 line:80%
It's only been two days,
but I missed you so much.

00:19:21.460 --> 00:19:24.421 line:80%
Why ride here
and not at the Royal Riding Grounds?

00:19:24.505 --> 00:19:25.839 line:80%
It is too confined there.

00:19:29.051 --> 00:19:30.761 line:80%
You could feel confined here too.

00:19:35.265 --> 00:19:36.308 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:19:36.976 --> 00:19:38.435 line:80%
[clicks tongue] Hyah!

00:19:40.229 --> 00:19:42.147 line:80%
-[horse whinnies]
-[chuckles]

00:19:42.773 --> 00:19:44.525 line:80%
-[clicks tongue]
-[horse whinnies]

00:19:45.985 --> 00:19:46.986 line:80%
Hyah!

00:20:03.460 --> 00:20:04.586 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:20:04.670 --> 00:20:05.796 line:80%
I missed you.

00:20:06.296 --> 00:20:08.757 line:80%
Even though I saw you yesterday. [giggles]

00:20:08.841 --> 00:20:09.925 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:20:12.469 --> 00:20:15.597 line:80%
But why are you having breakfast here
and not the Royal Dining Hall?

00:20:17.141 --> 00:20:19.560 line:80%
-I am taking some time off.
-Oh…

00:20:20.561 --> 00:20:21.937 line:80%
Me too. [giggles]

00:20:25.816 --> 00:20:27.693 line:80%
Are you off to volunteer
at the cat shelter?

00:20:27.776 --> 00:20:29.236 line:80%
To see Taekwon and Taegeuk?

00:20:31.071 --> 00:20:32.948 line:80%
You dared to run a background check on me?

00:20:33.032 --> 00:20:34.491 line:80%
-Yes.
-"Yes"?

00:20:35.075 --> 00:20:36.869 line:80%
You said you wanted to marry for love.

00:20:38.120 --> 00:20:39.121 line:80%
So?

00:20:39.204 --> 00:20:40.456 line:80%
So…

00:20:41.665 --> 00:20:43.042 line:80%
that is why I dare

00:20:43.876 --> 00:20:44.877 line:80%
to make a play

00:20:46.211 --> 00:20:47.671 line:80%
for Your Royal Highness's heart.

00:20:48.464 --> 00:20:50.424 line:80%
-[blows]
-[stammers]

00:20:51.967 --> 00:20:53.135 line:80%
[giggles]

00:20:57.639 --> 00:20:58.640 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:20:58.724 --> 00:21:00.642 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:21:00.726 --> 00:21:01.935 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:21:06.565 --> 00:21:07.733 line:80%
[horn honks]

00:21:16.283 --> 00:21:17.743 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:21:17.826 --> 00:21:19.787 line:80%
I missed you!

00:21:19.870 --> 00:21:20.913 line:80%
Where are you…

00:21:28.212 --> 00:21:29.213 line:80%
[sighs]

00:21:31.632 --> 00:21:33.008 line:80%
[giggles]

00:21:33.092 --> 00:21:35.010 line:80%
You can enjoy the movie.

00:21:36.303 --> 00:21:38.347 line:80%
I'll just enjoy watching you.

00:21:41.475 --> 00:21:42.476 line:80%
[sighs]

00:21:53.487 --> 00:21:54.696 line:80%
I missed you.

00:21:55.489 --> 00:21:56.573 line:80%
Should we run together?

00:21:59.034 --> 00:22:00.035 line:80%
Oh!

00:22:05.749 --> 00:22:07.000 line:80%
You're pretty fast!

00:22:07.626 --> 00:22:08.627 line:80%
[pants]

00:22:15.300 --> 00:22:17.136 line:80%
-What do you think?
-About what?

00:22:17.719 --> 00:22:20.389 line:80%
The outfit I am wearing right now.

00:22:20.472 --> 00:22:22.850 line:80%
Well, it's not bad…

00:22:22.933 --> 00:22:25.060 line:80%
"It's not bad"? That simply won't do.

00:22:25.144 --> 00:22:26.603 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:22:27.187 --> 00:22:30.274 line:80%
Just keeps popping up out of nowhere.

00:22:30.357 --> 00:22:32.818 line:80%
What keeps popping up out of nowhere?

00:22:33.527 --> 00:22:34.862 line:80%
I must have new garments made.

00:22:34.945 --> 00:22:36.446 line:80%
What? All of a sudden?

00:22:36.530 --> 00:22:39.867 line:80%
If I'm shadowed at every turn,
shouldn't I appear flawless at every step?

00:22:39.950 --> 00:22:41.451 line:80%
Wait, so who's shadowing you?

00:22:41.952 --> 00:22:43.120 line:80%
Get in.

00:22:43.203 --> 00:22:44.788 line:80%
Am I just talking to myself?

00:22:48.417 --> 00:22:50.669 line:80%
[yawns]

00:22:51.837 --> 00:22:52.838 line:80%
[groans]

00:22:54.423 --> 00:22:57.342 line:80%
[phone ringing]

00:22:57.426 --> 00:22:58.468 line:80%
GREMLIN

00:22:58.552 --> 00:23:01.054 line:80%
What a crappy way to start the day.

00:23:02.181 --> 00:23:03.182 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:23:06.101 --> 00:23:07.102 line:80%
What is it?

00:23:07.186 --> 00:23:09.396 line:80%
[Gremlin] <i>Huiju, you haven't forgotten</i>
<i>what today is, right?</i>

00:23:09.479 --> 00:23:10.814 line:80%
<i>I definitely did.</i>

00:23:10.898 --> 00:23:12.941 line:80%
That's why I'm calling to remind you.

00:23:13.025 --> 00:23:15.235 line:80%
You have your arranged date today.

00:23:16.236 --> 00:23:18.322 line:80%
Listen, Dayeong…

00:23:18.405 --> 00:23:19.406 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:23:19.489 --> 00:23:21.408 line:80%
I guess Father has high hopes for today.

00:23:21.491 --> 00:23:25.746 line:80%
He insisted that I go to your place
to help you with your outfit and makeup.

00:23:25.829 --> 00:23:28.957 line:80%
I spent ages trying to talk him out
of putting that pressure on you.

00:23:29.041 --> 00:23:31.668 line:80%
How incredibly thoughtful of you.

00:23:31.752 --> 00:23:33.170 line:80%
I know, right?

00:23:33.253 --> 00:23:35.547 line:80%
Huiju, do you think you'll need my help?

00:23:35.631 --> 00:23:37.257 line:80%
I can head over there right now.

00:23:37.341 --> 00:23:39.843 line:80%
Yeah, you should go.
She's going to need a lot of help.

00:23:39.927 --> 00:23:41.762 line:80%
-<i>Taeju?</i>
-You heard that?

00:23:41.845 --> 00:23:42.846 line:80%
-[gasps]
-[mutters]

00:23:42.930 --> 00:23:45.807 line:80%
What are you doing?
Shouldn't you be at work by now?

00:23:45.891 --> 00:23:49.686 line:80%
[chuckles] Huiju, I'll text you his number
and the meeting place again.

00:23:49.770 --> 00:23:50.771 line:80%
Be sure to check!

00:23:50.854 --> 00:23:52.147 line:80%
You know if you bail on him,

00:23:52.231 --> 00:23:54.816 line:80%
you'll put both Father and me
in a tough spot, right?

00:23:59.071 --> 00:24:01.490 line:80%
Geez, this damn Gremlin is unbelievable.

00:24:01.573 --> 00:24:02.574 line:80%
[phone notification]

00:24:04.910 --> 00:24:08.580 line:80%
[Dayeong] <i>Father is threatening to shut</i>
<i>down Castle Beauty if you bail again,</i>

00:24:08.664 --> 00:24:09.790 line:80%
<i>so watch out!</i>

00:24:10.374 --> 00:24:11.625 line:80%
<i>P.S. Kim Yeonjun.</i>

00:24:11.708 --> 00:24:14.169 line:80%
<i>Height, 180 cm.</i>
<i>I hear he's really handsome too.</i>

00:24:14.253 --> 00:24:15.254 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:17.089 --> 00:24:19.299 line:80%
-[line ringing]
-[sighs]

00:24:20.509 --> 00:24:21.593 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Mr. Kim Yeonjun?</i>

00:24:22.094 --> 00:24:24.346 line:80%
My apologies for the last-minute changes.

00:24:24.429 --> 00:24:26.556 line:80%
I wanted to take care of this quickly.

00:24:26.640 --> 00:24:28.976 line:80%
Not at all. I know how busy you are.

00:24:31.561 --> 00:24:34.106 line:80%
I heard a lot about you from my father.

00:24:35.065 --> 00:24:36.066 line:80%
Really?

00:24:36.566 --> 00:24:37.567 line:80%
Yes, I heard

00:24:38.151 --> 00:24:40.112 line:80%
that you possess both beauty and brains.

00:24:42.698 --> 00:24:45.742 line:80%
And that you have
a deep appreciation for art as well.

00:24:45.826 --> 00:24:47.786 line:80%
Hmm… I do?

00:24:48.412 --> 00:24:50.872 line:80%
Yes, don't you run an arts foundation?

00:24:50.956 --> 00:24:52.666 line:80%
Brilliantly, might I add.

00:24:52.749 --> 00:24:53.792 line:80%
Oh, that?

00:24:54.543 --> 00:24:56.795 line:80%
That's for money laundering purposes.

00:24:57.754 --> 00:24:59.089 line:80%
Brilliantly so.

00:25:00.382 --> 00:25:01.383 line:80%
Pardon?

00:25:02.426 --> 00:25:03.427 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:25:03.927 --> 00:25:05.053 line:80%
You know.

00:25:05.137 --> 00:25:06.138 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:25:09.474 --> 00:25:11.310 line:80%
When should we hold the wedding?

00:25:12.102 --> 00:25:13.979 line:80%
September? October?

00:25:14.062 --> 00:25:16.106 line:80%
[clears throat, coughs]

00:25:18.191 --> 00:25:19.735 line:80%
[clears throat] Pardon?

00:25:19.818 --> 00:25:22.154 line:80%
It's an arranged marriage anyway.

00:25:22.237 --> 00:25:23.739 line:80%
No reason to prolong it.

00:25:23.822 --> 00:25:24.906 line:80%
I see.

00:25:26.575 --> 00:25:27.909 line:80%
But shouldn't we at least--

00:25:27.993 --> 00:25:29.578 line:80%
Do you have siblings?

00:25:30.704 --> 00:25:31.747 line:80%
Only son?

00:25:32.539 --> 00:25:33.540 line:80%
Yes, I am.

00:25:34.333 --> 00:25:35.334 line:80%
I'm an only child.

00:25:35.417 --> 00:25:36.668 line:80%
Mmm…

00:25:36.752 --> 00:25:37.753 line:80%
That's nice.

00:25:38.795 --> 00:25:41.256 line:80%
No siblings to fight over the inheritance.

00:25:44.217 --> 00:25:45.969 line:80%
PRIVATE COLLECTION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

00:25:54.102 --> 00:25:56.021 line:80%
I have an older brother.

00:25:57.731 --> 00:25:59.316 line:80%
You know Director Seong Taeju?

00:25:59.816 --> 00:26:02.319 line:80%
Yes, I met him last time
at a shareholders' meeting.

00:26:02.402 --> 00:26:06.490 line:80%
My father simply adores him.

00:26:06.573 --> 00:26:08.784 line:80%
He'll likely succeed
my father as chairman.

00:26:09.534 --> 00:26:11.286 line:80%
And you're a part of that plan.

00:26:12.204 --> 00:26:13.205 line:80%
Me?

00:26:13.705 --> 00:26:14.915 line:80%
How am I a part of that?

00:26:14.998 --> 00:26:16.708 line:80%
He doesn't want to give me leverage.

00:26:17.709 --> 00:26:19.586 line:80%
I'm already good at my job.

00:26:20.253 --> 00:26:23.131 line:80%
He knows if I marry
into a powerful family on top of that,

00:26:23.215 --> 00:26:25.592 line:80%
the first thing I'll do is
kick my brother to the curb.

00:26:27.010 --> 00:26:28.595 line:80%
I see. [scoffs]

00:26:32.849 --> 00:26:34.935 line:80%
PRIVATE COLLECTION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

00:26:35.018 --> 00:26:37.312 line:80%
Is he a cat lover or something?

00:26:44.319 --> 00:26:45.612 line:80%
Do you think you can do it?

00:26:46.446 --> 00:26:48.782 line:80%
-Pardon?
-If you're interested in marrying me,

00:26:49.449 --> 00:26:51.743 line:80%
money must be what you're after.

00:26:52.702 --> 00:26:54.246 line:80%
I can do that.

00:26:55.539 --> 00:26:57.457 line:80%
Whatever sum you have in mind,

00:26:58.208 --> 00:27:00.168 line:80%
I can give you far more than that.

00:27:01.420 --> 00:27:04.297 line:80%
What about you? Can you do your part?

00:27:04.381 --> 00:27:06.925 line:80%
Are you willing to devote
all of yourself to me…

00:27:14.057 --> 00:27:15.892 line:80%
so I can get all the way to the top?

00:27:18.854 --> 00:27:19.855 line:80%
[Hyeon] Ms. Seong?

00:27:21.064 --> 00:27:22.065 line:80%
Aide Choi.

00:27:22.149 --> 00:27:24.526 line:80%
-Hello.
-Hello there.

00:27:24.609 --> 00:27:26.278 line:80%
You must be here for the exhibit.

00:27:26.361 --> 00:27:29.698 line:80%
Yes. I wanted to see for myself
how impressive the Royal Collection was.

00:27:29.781 --> 00:27:31.575 line:80%
I see. Is it to your liking?

00:27:32.242 --> 00:27:33.410 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:27:33.493 --> 00:27:34.578 line:80%
It's not bad.

00:27:34.661 --> 00:27:36.163 line:80%
I'd steal a few if I could.

00:27:36.246 --> 00:27:38.582 line:80%
Then you should go to basement level two.

00:27:38.665 --> 00:27:41.126 line:80%
-The expensive stuff is there.
-[laughs]

00:27:41.209 --> 00:27:42.335 line:80%
Aide Choi.

00:27:42.919 --> 00:27:44.045 line:80%
Coming.

00:27:44.129 --> 00:27:45.422 line:80%
Please excuse me.

00:27:45.505 --> 00:27:46.756 line:80%
Enjoy the exhibit.

00:27:48.383 --> 00:27:49.384 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:27:52.053 --> 00:27:54.848 line:80%
I'm sorry. I should've introduced you.

00:27:59.102 --> 00:28:00.103 line:80%
Huiju.

00:28:06.109 --> 00:28:08.111 line:80%
[♪ contemplative music plays]

00:28:10.197 --> 00:28:12.199 line:80%
I don't think this marriage would work.

00:28:14.784 --> 00:28:16.578 line:80%
Not the least bit surprised.

00:28:18.205 --> 00:28:19.206 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:28:21.500 --> 00:28:22.959 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:27.881 --> 00:28:29.090 line:80%
[meows]

00:28:30.050 --> 00:28:32.427 line:80%
-Who?
-Ms. Seong Huiju.

00:28:32.511 --> 00:28:34.012 line:80%
The one who proposed to you.

00:28:35.180 --> 00:28:38.058 line:80%
Gosh, as soon as you turned her down,

00:28:38.141 --> 00:28:39.684 line:80%
she found herself a new man.

00:28:39.768 --> 00:28:42.270 line:80%
She's so cool. So cool.

00:28:42.354 --> 00:28:43.772 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-[scoffs]

00:28:44.439 --> 00:28:45.440 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:28:46.691 --> 00:28:50.946 line:80%
To be honest, I was worried she might be
one of the Queen Mother's people.

00:28:51.029 --> 00:28:52.405 line:80%
You have quite the imagination.

00:28:53.073 --> 00:28:54.324 line:80%
Her Majesty and Seong Huiju?

00:28:54.407 --> 00:28:56.034 line:80%
Why not? It's a possibility.

00:28:56.117 --> 00:28:57.661 line:80%
[scoffs] "Why not"?

00:28:59.538 --> 00:29:01.039 line:80%
Move it more to the right.

00:29:02.415 --> 00:29:03.875 line:80%
More to the right?

00:29:05.919 --> 00:29:06.920 line:80%
Up.

00:29:07.003 --> 00:29:08.088 line:80%
Down.

00:29:08.171 --> 00:29:10.048 line:80%
Up, up, down.

00:29:11.633 --> 00:29:12.676 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:29:12.759 --> 00:29:13.843 line:80%
Original spot.

00:29:13.927 --> 00:29:15.011 line:80%
[groans]

00:29:18.557 --> 00:29:21.601 line:80%
My sister-in-law hails from a family
that has produced four queens.

00:29:23.687 --> 00:29:25.814 line:80%
<i>Few people truly grasp</i>
<i>how towering that pride</i>

00:29:26.898 --> 00:29:28.316 line:80%
<i>and sense of superiority is.</i>

00:29:29.651 --> 00:29:30.652 line:80%
<i>A person like her,</i>

00:29:31.528 --> 00:29:33.572 line:80%
colluding with Huiju, a mere commoner?

00:29:34.698 --> 00:29:35.699 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:29:38.660 --> 00:29:40.996 line:80%
[Hyeon] Who would win between the two?

00:29:43.373 --> 00:29:44.499 line:80%
Well, you see…

00:29:44.583 --> 00:29:45.875 line:80%
[sniffs, chuckles]

00:29:45.959 --> 00:29:47.711 line:80%
I did a little digging into Ms. Seong.

00:29:47.794 --> 00:29:48.878 line:80%
-Choi Hyeon.
-I mean,

00:29:48.962 --> 00:29:50.880 line:80%
it wasn't a proper investigation
or anything.

00:29:50.964 --> 00:29:53.466 line:80%
It was just a light inquiry.

00:29:54.884 --> 00:29:57.554 line:80%
[sighs] You have to admit
it was a bit strange.

00:29:57.637 --> 00:29:59.806 line:80%
She just showed up out of nowhere
and proposed.

00:29:59.889 --> 00:30:01.516 line:80%
-So?
-I found that

00:30:01.600 --> 00:30:03.018 line:80%
there was nothing special to note.

00:30:03.101 --> 00:30:06.187 line:80%
She only leaves the house to go to work.

00:30:06.271 --> 00:30:08.398 line:80%
She doesn't seem to have
too many friends either.

00:30:08.481 --> 00:30:11.026 line:80%
She eats with her assistant
and goes to the movies with her.

00:30:11.109 --> 00:30:12.402 line:80%
Wait!

00:30:12.485 --> 00:30:13.987 line:80%
Maybe it's because of her temper?

00:30:14.863 --> 00:30:16.865 line:80%
-Her temper?
-You didn't know?

00:30:16.948 --> 00:30:19.284 line:80%
I heard she was known
for being a hothead in school.

00:30:19.367 --> 00:30:22.203 line:80%
It's harder to find someone
who hasn't fought her. [laughs]

00:30:22.829 --> 00:30:23.830 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:30:23.913 --> 00:30:25.790 line:80%
I hear she never lost a fight either.

00:30:27.709 --> 00:30:28.710 line:80%
Aren't you curious?

00:30:29.919 --> 00:30:30.920 line:80%
About what?

00:30:31.004 --> 00:30:34.049 line:80%
As you said,
the Queen Mother and Ms. Seong

00:30:34.132 --> 00:30:35.759 line:80%
could not be any more different.

00:30:35.842 --> 00:30:38.720 line:80%
Of course, if rank is in play,
the outcome is obvious.

00:30:38.803 --> 00:30:41.181 line:80%
But strip away the hierarchy?

00:30:41.264 --> 00:30:42.974 line:80%
It'll be like "Pow!" With a bit of…

00:30:43.058 --> 00:30:45.769 line:80%
[imitating explosions]

00:30:48.104 --> 00:30:49.147 line:80%
My apologies.

00:30:56.488 --> 00:30:58.782 line:80%
[door opens, closes]

00:31:00.909 --> 00:31:03.203 line:80%
[♪ contemplative music plays]

00:31:03.286 --> 00:31:04.371 line:80%
[sighs]

00:31:19.511 --> 00:31:21.763 line:80%
[Yun] <i>Have you truly gone mad?</i>

00:31:31.690 --> 00:31:34.901 line:80%
I INTEND TO STEP DOWN
FROM THE THRONE…

00:31:35.485 --> 00:31:36.486 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:31:53.336 --> 00:31:55.255 line:80%
It will be better than dying.

00:31:55.338 --> 00:31:56.339 line:80%
[gasps]

00:32:05.265 --> 00:32:07.100 line:80%
It would be better to die.

00:32:11.938 --> 00:32:13.398 line:80%
I would rather see you dead.

00:32:15.066 --> 00:32:16.359 line:80%
[sighs]

00:32:23.199 --> 00:32:25.160 line:80%
For the sake of the Crown Prince.

00:32:38.548 --> 00:32:39.549 line:80%
My Queen.

00:32:54.230 --> 00:32:55.857 line:80%
My Queen!

00:32:59.152 --> 00:33:01.070 line:80%
-Fire!
-It's a fire!

00:33:01.154 --> 00:33:04.073 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:33:23.802 --> 00:33:25.970 line:80%
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:33:26.054 --> 00:33:28.598 line:80%
-Your Majesty…
-[sobbing]

00:33:29.849 --> 00:33:31.100 line:80%
Your Majesty…

00:33:32.227 --> 00:33:33.561 line:80%
Your Majesty…

00:33:59.337 --> 00:34:00.922 line:80%
Where is the Crown Prince?

00:34:01.548 --> 00:34:02.549 line:80%
Huh?

00:34:03.383 --> 00:34:05.009 line:80%
Where is my nephew…

00:34:07.136 --> 00:34:08.555 line:80%
the heir to the throne?

00:34:11.099 --> 00:34:12.100 line:80%
[gasps]

00:34:12.976 --> 00:34:14.477 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:34:42.714 --> 00:34:43.756 line:80%
[sighs]

00:34:51.598 --> 00:34:53.057 line:80%
Did you sleep poorly again?

00:35:04.569 --> 00:35:06.988 line:80%
You can't keep going without sleep.

00:35:14.662 --> 00:35:17.540 line:80%
Do you know what you will
be doing today, Your Majesty?

00:35:18.207 --> 00:35:20.585 line:80%
I am to present the Flowers of Honor.

00:35:21.169 --> 00:35:24.923 line:80%
The recipients are your valued subjects
who lead the nation's industries.

00:35:25.548 --> 00:35:27.717 line:80%
They are Your Majesty's trusty workhorses.

00:35:28.217 --> 00:35:29.218 line:80%
Hence,

00:35:30.511 --> 00:35:32.430 line:80%
you must carry yourself with dignity.

00:35:36.017 --> 00:35:37.894 line:80%
When is I-AN set to return?

00:35:37.977 --> 00:35:40.146 line:80%
I believe he is to return in four days.

00:35:42.065 --> 00:35:43.191 line:80%
This is your opportunity.

00:35:43.274 --> 00:35:45.777 line:80%
You must show the world
you can do it on your own.

00:35:45.860 --> 00:35:47.820 line:80%
Without I-AN by your side.

00:35:48.529 --> 00:35:49.906 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:35:52.200 --> 00:35:53.201 line:80%
Yes.

00:35:57.997 --> 00:35:59.082 line:80%
[Hyeon] He'll be fine, right?

00:35:59.582 --> 00:36:00.750 line:80%
No, he won't.

00:36:00.833 --> 00:36:03.294 line:80%
How can you say that? You're his uncle.

00:36:04.003 --> 00:36:05.296 line:80%
I know because I'm his uncle.

00:36:06.381 --> 00:36:09.384 line:80%
I know that my nephew is but a mere child.

00:36:10.009 --> 00:36:13.554 line:80%
Then perhaps you can go
and lend him your support.

00:36:15.264 --> 00:36:17.892 line:80%
-Why should I?
-You said he is just a child.

00:36:19.018 --> 00:36:20.436 line:80%
Why are you sweating so much?

00:36:21.270 --> 00:36:22.355 line:80%
Are you feeling unwell?

00:36:23.606 --> 00:36:25.400 line:80%
[phone buzzes]

00:36:26.359 --> 00:36:28.695 line:80%
Yes, I'm listening.

00:36:30.738 --> 00:36:32.991 line:80%
All right, I get it.

00:36:35.076 --> 00:36:36.661 line:80%
DOBBY

00:36:36.744 --> 00:36:39.372 line:80%
[Ms. Do] <i>You have to be</i>
<i>at the venue by 11,</i>

00:36:39.455 --> 00:36:40.915 line:80%
<i>so no dawdling please.</i>

00:36:40.999 --> 00:36:42.625 line:80%
<i>Have you eaten?</i>

00:36:42.709 --> 00:36:45.169 line:80%
<i>You won't have time to eat,</i>
<i>so eat something beforehand.</i>

00:36:45.712 --> 00:36:47.547 line:80%
<i>There will be reporters everywhere.</i>

00:36:47.630 --> 00:36:49.215 line:80%
<i>A lot of eyes will be on you.</i>

00:36:49.298 --> 00:36:50.883 line:80%
<i>You know if you cause a scene,</i>

00:36:50.967 --> 00:36:52.677 line:80%
<i>I'll be stuck working all night, right?</i>

00:36:53.720 --> 00:36:55.930 line:80%
<i>Your dry-cleaned outfit is on the hanger.</i>

00:36:57.515 --> 00:36:58.891 line:80%
<i>No red.</i>

00:37:02.979 --> 00:37:04.397 line:80%
-<i>No strong perfume.</i>
-[sighs]

00:37:06.024 --> 00:37:07.025 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:37:07.692 --> 00:37:10.820 line:80%
-<i>No flashy accessories. Got it?</i>
-[exclaims]

00:37:11.612 --> 00:37:13.990 line:80%
I bought you for this exact purpose.

00:37:14.073 --> 00:37:16.159 line:80%
<i>Don't even. I told you nothing flashy.</i>

00:37:17.702 --> 00:37:18.995 line:80%
Are we on a video call?

00:37:23.458 --> 00:37:24.542 line:80%
[mutters]

00:37:42.185 --> 00:37:44.145 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:37:48.566 --> 00:37:51.402 line:80%
2025 ECONOMIC HONORS OF KOREA

00:37:55.323 --> 00:37:57.408 line:80%
This is how they treat their honorees?

00:37:58.117 --> 00:38:00.453 line:80%
Lower your voice.
There are lots of reporters around.

00:38:00.536 --> 00:38:03.664 line:80%
Seriously? If anything,
they should be boosting my morale.

00:38:03.748 --> 00:38:04.999 line:80%
Are they trying to crush it?

00:38:05.083 --> 00:38:07.752 line:80%
His Majesty the King is coming.
What choice do we have?

00:38:07.835 --> 00:38:09.670 line:80%
Right, so why did he need to be here?

00:38:09.754 --> 00:38:11.214 line:80%
Just enjoy cookies at the palace.

00:38:11.297 --> 00:38:12.715 line:80%
-Stop it.
-All right!

00:38:14.675 --> 00:38:15.968 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:23.392 --> 00:38:24.644 line:80%
[secretary] Your Majesty.

00:38:24.727 --> 00:38:26.604 line:80%
You do not need to be nervous.

00:38:26.687 --> 00:38:29.816 line:80%
You have us by your side. [chuckles]

00:38:30.483 --> 00:38:31.984 line:80%
Would Your Majesty like a snack?

00:38:32.985 --> 00:38:36.739 line:80%
Can we review the order
of the ceremony again?

00:38:37.448 --> 00:38:40.868 line:80%
Looking at that
will only make you more nervous.

00:38:40.952 --> 00:38:43.704 line:80%
Once you step up onto the podium,
we'll take care of everything.

00:38:44.622 --> 00:38:45.998 line:80%
[secretary chuckles]

00:38:46.082 --> 00:38:47.083 line:80%
[sighs]

00:38:47.708 --> 00:38:48.709 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:38:51.712 --> 00:38:52.713 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:38:56.968 --> 00:38:58.010 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:38:59.554 --> 00:39:01.264 line:80%
You dare stand in my way?

00:39:02.932 --> 00:39:04.267 line:80%
No, I wasn't…

00:39:04.350 --> 00:39:06.519 line:80%
Then do you stand in His Majesty's way?

00:39:16.487 --> 00:39:18.364 line:80%
The aides have been
negligent in their duties.

00:39:19.949 --> 00:39:22.243 line:80%
Both protocol and security
are woefully inadequate.

00:39:23.286 --> 00:39:24.954 line:80%
My apologies, Your Royal Highness.

00:39:28.416 --> 00:39:31.419 line:80%
INCOMING CALL

00:39:31.502 --> 00:39:33.546 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:39:34.297 --> 00:39:35.298 line:80%
[sighs]

00:39:41.721 --> 00:39:42.930 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:39:43.014 --> 00:39:44.307 line:80%
[Yun] <i>Uncle.</i>

00:39:46.225 --> 00:39:48.269 line:80%
I am scared, Uncle.

00:39:50.563 --> 00:39:51.856 line:80%
[sighs]

00:39:55.401 --> 00:39:56.569 line:80%
[sighs]

00:40:02.992 --> 00:40:04.076 line:80%
Thus,

00:40:04.702 --> 00:40:07.955 line:80%
I have come to fulfill my duty
as your loyal subject, Your Majesty.

00:40:10.333 --> 00:40:12.084 line:80%
[indistinct chattering]

00:40:16.714 --> 00:40:20.134 line:80%
[secretary] Announcing His Majesty!

00:40:21.093 --> 00:40:24.472 line:80%
[camera shutters clicking]

00:40:53.376 --> 00:40:55.044 line:80%
Take my hand, Your Majesty.

00:40:57.171 --> 00:40:59.173 line:80%
[♪ uplifting music plays]

00:41:26.867 --> 00:41:28.995 line:80%
Next, we have
the Global Entrepreneur Award.

00:41:29.078 --> 00:41:32.248 line:80%
Chairman Park Jeseung.
Please give him a warm round of applause.

00:41:41.090 --> 00:41:44.093 line:80%
Next, we have the Best Entrepreneur Award.

00:41:44.176 --> 00:41:48.222 line:80%
Castle Beauty's Seong Huiju.

00:41:50.391 --> 00:41:53.811 line:80%
Castle Beauty remains at the forefront
of the global K-beauty craze,

00:41:53.894 --> 00:41:57.732 line:80%
showcasing Korea's advanced technology
and refined beauty.

00:41:57.815 --> 00:41:59.483 line:80%
Guided by the slogan "Eco Beauty,"

00:41:59.567 --> 00:42:02.820 line:80%
they remain dedicated
to creating eco-friendly products.

00:42:07.366 --> 00:42:08.367 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:42:08.868 --> 00:42:10.494 line:80%
Can you place it on my head?

00:42:12.621 --> 00:42:13.706 line:80%
Right here.

00:42:15.207 --> 00:42:16.208 line:80%
[sighs]

00:42:19.337 --> 00:42:20.629 line:80%
[applause]

00:42:22.965 --> 00:42:24.759 line:80%
I am deeply honored, Your Majesty.

00:42:24.842 --> 00:42:26.010 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:42:30.848 --> 00:42:32.308 line:80%
The nation rejoices

00:42:33.184 --> 00:42:34.602 line:80%
in the beauty of your talent.

00:42:37.688 --> 00:42:38.898 line:80%
I missed you.

00:42:42.068 --> 00:42:44.111 line:80%
Will there be a prize as well?

00:42:45.905 --> 00:42:47.531 line:80%
I believe it is already on your head.

00:42:48.699 --> 00:42:50.701 line:80%
This is from His Majesty.

00:42:51.410 --> 00:42:53.037 line:80%
There is something else I would like

00:42:54.163 --> 00:42:55.539 line:80%
from Your Royal Highness.

00:42:56.165 --> 00:42:57.166 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:42:58.834 --> 00:42:59.835 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:42:59.919 --> 00:43:02.254 line:80%
[host] She is a young leader
representing the nation.

00:43:02.338 --> 00:43:05.966 line:80%
CEO Seong Huiju.
Please give her a warm round of applause.

00:43:23.317 --> 00:43:24.318 line:80%
[inhales sharply]

00:43:30.574 --> 00:43:31.575 line:80%
[giggles]

00:43:32.743 --> 00:43:33.744 line:80%
Ready?

00:43:40.084 --> 00:43:41.335 line:80%
-Got it?
-Yes, got it.

00:43:41.419 --> 00:43:42.420 line:80%
Okay.

00:43:44.422 --> 00:43:45.423 line:80%
[sighs]

00:43:45.506 --> 00:43:48.717 line:80%
"Hashtag Flower of Honor."

00:43:49.301 --> 00:43:51.053 line:20%
"Best Company."

00:43:51.137 --> 00:43:53.222 line:20%
"Castle Beauty."

00:43:53.305 --> 00:43:55.141 line:20%
"Hashtag…

00:43:57.560 --> 00:43:59.979 line:20%
Grand Prince I-AN."

00:44:02.481 --> 00:44:04.066 line:80%
[chuckles] Let's go.

00:44:06.819 --> 00:44:07.903 line:20%
PRIME MINISTER MIN JEONGWOO

00:44:07.987 --> 00:44:10.239 line:20%
-[knocks on door]
-[Jeongwoo] Come in.

00:44:10.322 --> 00:44:12.158 line:80%
[door opens, closes]

00:44:15.494 --> 00:44:16.495 line:80%
Sir.

00:44:16.579 --> 00:44:18.330 line:80%
The Economic Honors event went smoothly.

00:44:19.206 --> 00:44:20.207 line:20%
Really?

00:44:20.916 --> 00:44:23.127 line:80%
Our young Sovereign is all grown up now.

00:44:23.752 --> 00:44:26.046 line:20%
Grand Prince I-AN accompanied him.

00:44:27.047 --> 00:44:28.757 line:20%
-Isn't he on leave?
-Yes.

00:44:28.841 --> 00:44:31.969 line:80%
It was a last-minute decision
after His Majesty made a personal request.

00:44:32.052 --> 00:44:33.512 line:80%
Hmm…

00:44:37.850 --> 00:44:39.101 line:80%
PRINCE I-AN'S
SURPRISE APPEARANCE

00:44:39.185 --> 00:44:40.311 line:80%
AT 2025 ECONOMIC HONORS…

00:44:44.106 --> 00:44:46.817 line:80%
CASTLE BEAUTY'S SEONG HUIJU
RECEIVES BEST ENTREPRENEUR AWARD

00:44:49.570 --> 00:44:50.571 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:44:52.990 --> 00:44:54.867 line:80%
-[grunts]
-Are you going somewhere?

00:44:54.950 --> 00:44:56.285 line:80%
I'm clocking out.

00:44:56.368 --> 00:44:57.786 line:80%
Already?

00:44:57.870 --> 00:44:58.871 line:80%
I'm done.

00:45:03.250 --> 00:45:05.461 line:80%
And maybe a bit quicker next time.

00:45:06.378 --> 00:45:07.379 line:80%
Pardon?

00:45:07.463 --> 00:45:09.757 line:80%
If you tell me after the fact,
where does that leave me?

00:45:11.842 --> 00:45:13.552 line:80%
-My apologies, sir.
-[chuckles]

00:45:27.316 --> 00:45:28.692 line:80%
Get back safely, Your Majesty.

00:45:29.276 --> 00:45:31.904 line:80%
Are you not coming with me?

00:45:32.947 --> 00:45:35.032 line:80%
I am still on leave.

00:45:36.700 --> 00:45:39.537 line:80%
Your Majesty, the Queen Mother is waiting.

00:45:42.915 --> 00:45:43.958 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:54.635 --> 00:45:55.636 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:46:04.103 --> 00:46:05.104 line:80%
[sighs]

00:46:08.566 --> 00:46:09.567 line:80%
Are you all right?

00:46:13.654 --> 00:46:14.822 line:80%
[gasps] Take this.

00:46:16.156 --> 00:46:17.157 line:80%
This too.

00:46:18.701 --> 00:46:21.579 line:80%
-Wait, hold on. Give me that too.
-Why?

00:46:21.662 --> 00:46:24.582 line:80%
Are you actually wearing that hat
to your hotel staycation?

00:46:24.665 --> 00:46:25.916 line:80%
-Yeah.
-Seriously?

00:46:26.667 --> 00:46:27.710 line:80%
[sighs]

00:46:27.793 --> 00:46:30.004 line:80%
Don't tell people
you're the CEO of Castle Beauty.

00:46:30.087 --> 00:46:31.422 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:46:31.505 --> 00:46:34.383 line:80%
[chuckles] They all know already.

00:46:35.467 --> 00:46:37.219 line:80%
Don't call me unless it's urgent.

00:46:37.303 --> 00:46:39.179 line:80%
It's been ages since I've had time off.

00:46:39.805 --> 00:46:42.558 line:80%
Me too. Me too.

00:46:42.641 --> 00:46:44.059 line:80%
-Go.
-I'm off.

00:46:47.146 --> 00:46:48.147 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:46:49.815 --> 00:46:50.899 line:80%
Oh.

00:46:50.983 --> 00:46:51.984 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:46:53.694 --> 00:46:54.778 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:47:01.952 --> 00:47:03.245 line:80%
Order everything.

00:47:03.329 --> 00:47:05.039 line:80%
I am a winner of the Flower of Honor.

00:47:05.122 --> 00:47:07.041 line:80%
It'll be my treat today. [chuckles]

00:47:07.124 --> 00:47:08.542 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:47:08.626 --> 00:47:09.627 line:80%
No.

00:47:09.710 --> 00:47:12.046 line:80%
Let me treat you today
to congratulate you.

00:47:12.129 --> 00:47:13.922 line:80%
I told you I'd treat you last time.

00:47:14.965 --> 00:47:17.718 line:80%
Now that's an offer I never turn down.

00:47:17.801 --> 00:47:18.927 line:80%
Score.

00:47:19.511 --> 00:47:20.763 line:80%
[chuckles, inhales sharply]

00:47:22.431 --> 00:47:23.557 line:80%
Hmm…

00:47:28.187 --> 00:47:31.315 line:80%
Just take it off for the meal.

00:47:31.398 --> 00:47:32.483 line:80%
Why?

00:47:33.067 --> 00:47:34.818 line:80%
Jealous? [scoffs]

00:47:34.902 --> 00:47:36.570 line:80%
It's embarrassing.

00:47:37.154 --> 00:47:38.572 line:80%
You look like a giant pineapple.

00:47:38.656 --> 00:47:39.948 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:47:40.032 --> 00:47:42.451 line:80%
Are you sure
it's not a really pretty pineapple?

00:47:43.035 --> 00:47:44.119 line:80%
Definitely not.

00:47:45.079 --> 00:47:46.080 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:47:51.710 --> 00:47:52.920 line:80%
[sighs]

00:48:02.137 --> 00:48:04.431 line:80%
Moments like this remind me
you haven't changed at all.

00:48:04.515 --> 00:48:06.308 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:48:06.392 --> 00:48:09.269 line:80%
You used to get the Flower of Honor
all the time in school.

00:48:09.353 --> 00:48:12.231 line:80%
For your grades and artwork…

00:48:14.024 --> 00:48:15.192 line:80%
What else was there?

00:48:16.777 --> 00:48:17.903 line:80%
Archery?

00:48:18.779 --> 00:48:20.197 line:80%
Archery. [chuckles]

00:48:20.280 --> 00:48:22.282 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:48:30.082 --> 00:48:32.084 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[sighs]

00:48:32.167 --> 00:48:35.337 line:80%
How were you even chosen
to represent Jujak House?

00:48:35.421 --> 00:48:38.173 line:80%
-I had to change my grip yesterday…
-[groans]

00:48:39.091 --> 00:48:40.551 line:80%
Activate your core.

00:48:41.635 --> 00:48:43.303 line:80%
Chin down.

00:48:43.387 --> 00:48:44.388 line:80%
Chest.

00:48:45.013 --> 00:48:46.014 line:80%
Chest.

00:48:48.225 --> 00:48:49.226 line:80%
Draw your bow.

00:48:54.898 --> 00:48:56.483 line:80%
Shoulders back further.

00:49:00.654 --> 00:49:01.739 line:80%
Right by your lips.

00:49:07.619 --> 00:49:08.620 line:80%
Focus!

00:49:09.705 --> 00:49:11.331 line:80%
Right. Focus.

00:49:12.624 --> 00:49:14.710 line:80%
-[clears throat]
-I swear

00:49:16.044 --> 00:49:19.506 line:80%
there will be hell to pay
if we lose because of you.

00:49:21.425 --> 00:49:23.135 line:80%
-Focus!
-Huh?

00:49:24.052 --> 00:49:25.429 line:80%
Right, focus.

00:49:25.929 --> 00:49:27.097 line:80%
Keep pulling

00:49:28.182 --> 00:49:29.183 line:80%
and shoot.

00:49:30.184 --> 00:49:34.062 line:80%
Thank goodness
you were at least book smart.

00:49:34.646 --> 00:49:36.356 line:80%
-Me?
-You're bad at everything else.

00:49:36.440 --> 00:49:38.901 line:80%
[chuckles] Seriously? Me?

00:49:38.984 --> 00:49:42.738 line:80%
You're not like running the country
into the ground or anything, right?

00:49:43.822 --> 00:49:45.532 line:80%
If something feels off,

00:49:45.616 --> 00:49:48.285 line:80%
don't be afraid to ask questions.
No need to feel embarrassed.

00:49:48.368 --> 00:49:49.828 line:80%
Don't try to do it alone.

00:49:49.912 --> 00:49:51.079 line:80%
All right.

00:49:51.789 --> 00:49:52.956 line:80%
Just order already.

00:49:54.208 --> 00:49:55.209 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:49:55.959 --> 00:49:58.587 line:80%
Let's see here.

00:50:00.923 --> 00:50:03.926 line:80%
What should I have?

00:50:07.846 --> 00:50:09.431 line:80%
PHARMACY

00:50:11.809 --> 00:50:12.893 line:80%
Hello.

00:50:12.976 --> 00:50:14.019 line:80%
Welcome.

00:50:14.102 --> 00:50:16.814 line:80%
What should someone take
if they have a really bad headache,

00:50:16.897 --> 00:50:19.274 line:80%
a slight fever,
and keep breaking out in a cold sweat?

00:50:19.358 --> 00:50:21.360 line:80%
Just a moment. I'll grab what you need.

00:50:21.443 --> 00:50:23.695 line:80%
Okay. Please hurry.

00:50:24.696 --> 00:50:25.697 line:80%
[sighs]

00:50:34.957 --> 00:50:35.958 line:80%
[sighs]

00:50:44.341 --> 00:50:45.342 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:50:55.686 --> 00:50:56.687 line:80%
Once the fever breaks,

00:50:56.770 --> 00:50:58.689 line:80%
we should take you
to Royal Seoul Hospital.

00:50:58.772 --> 00:51:00.983 line:80%
I think it'd be best
to have you checked out there.

00:51:02.317 --> 00:51:04.444 line:80%
It's crawling
with the Queen Mother's brothers.

00:51:04.528 --> 00:51:06.196 line:80%
Don't stir up trouble.

00:51:06.738 --> 00:51:08.949 line:80%
[sighs] Understood.

00:51:09.032 --> 00:51:10.367 line:80%
Have you notified my household?

00:51:11.118 --> 00:51:12.119 line:80%
Yes.

00:51:12.202 --> 00:51:14.454 line:80%
I told them you'd be
staying the night at a hotel.

00:51:14.538 --> 00:51:17.040 line:80%
I didn't say anything
about you being sick. Don't worry.

00:51:21.503 --> 00:51:22.880 line:80%
[sighs]

00:51:26.049 --> 00:51:27.843 line:80%
[automated voice] <i>The doors are opening.</i>

00:51:28.635 --> 00:51:29.720 line:80%
[sighs]

00:51:32.514 --> 00:51:34.349 line:20%
SHE LOOKS SO DAMN GOOD

00:51:34.433 --> 00:51:37.227 line:20%
Our stock is going to skyrocket tomorrow.

00:51:39.146 --> 00:51:40.188 line:80%
Oh, my goodness.

00:51:40.272 --> 00:51:41.273 line:80%
Oh, my.

00:51:41.899 --> 00:51:43.525 line:80%
-Ms. Seong?
-Aide Choi?

00:51:44.067 --> 00:51:45.527 line:80%
-Hello.
-Yes, hello.

00:51:55.829 --> 00:51:57.372 line:80%
You don't need to worry too much.

00:51:58.248 --> 00:52:02.377 line:80%
However, I do wonder
if he typically has trouble sleeping.

00:52:03.211 --> 00:52:04.212 line:80%
Uh…

00:52:04.796 --> 00:52:08.050 line:80%
Yes, he suffers from a bit of insomnia.

00:52:08.133 --> 00:52:11.553 line:80%
[doctor] It's hard to recover from fatigue
if you can't sleep.

00:52:12.262 --> 00:52:14.723 line:80%
Sleeping aids should help.

00:52:14.806 --> 00:52:17.100 line:80%
Make sure he gets a prescription
and gets some sleep.

00:52:17.184 --> 00:52:18.518 line:80%
All right. Thank you, doctor.

00:52:32.699 --> 00:52:33.951 line:80%
Doctor.

00:52:34.534 --> 00:52:36.495 line:80%
Thank you for coming at a late hour.

00:52:36.578 --> 00:52:38.163 line:80%
[chuckles] No need to thank me.

00:52:38.956 --> 00:52:39.998 line:80%
For the record,

00:52:41.166 --> 00:52:43.752 line:80%
can we say I was the patient today?

00:52:44.419 --> 00:52:46.922 line:80%
-Pardon?
-You know I get hurt all the time.

00:52:48.173 --> 00:52:49.800 line:80%
You were here to see me

00:52:50.509 --> 00:52:52.344 line:80%
and only me today.

00:52:53.345 --> 00:52:54.346 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:56.056 --> 00:52:57.182 line:80%
Understood, Ms. Seong.

00:52:57.265 --> 00:52:58.266 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:58.934 --> 00:52:59.935 line:80%
Get back safely.

00:53:00.602 --> 00:53:01.603 line:80%
Take care.

00:53:06.149 --> 00:53:07.609 line:80%
PRINCE I-AN'S
SURPRISE APPEARANCE

00:53:07.693 --> 00:53:09.027 line:80%
AT ECONOMIC HONORS…

00:53:15.283 --> 00:53:16.702 line:80%
[sighs]

00:53:17.995 --> 00:53:20.998 line:80%
Did you forget I told you
to carry yourself with dignity?

00:53:21.623 --> 00:53:25.502 line:80%
U-Uncle…

00:53:25.585 --> 00:53:27.170 line:80%
Do not call him that!

00:53:32.634 --> 00:53:34.845 line:80%
Please do not let it upset you.

00:53:35.595 --> 00:53:38.015 line:80%
His Majesty is still very young.

00:53:41.268 --> 00:53:43.520 line:80%
How truly contemptible.

00:53:44.479 --> 00:53:45.480 line:80%
Pardon?

00:53:48.025 --> 00:53:50.068 line:80%
I speak of that feeble bloodline.

00:53:52.070 --> 00:53:55.991 line:80%
<i>He was the very likeness</i>
<i>of the late king at that moment.</i>

00:53:59.036 --> 00:54:00.620 line:80%
It sends a chill down my spine.

00:54:02.622 --> 00:54:03.623 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:07.753 --> 00:54:09.713 line:80%
Have you located I-AN?

00:54:09.796 --> 00:54:11.548 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:54:17.596 --> 00:54:18.597 line:80%
Aide Choi.

00:54:19.264 --> 00:54:20.432 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:54:20.515 --> 00:54:21.850 line:80%
You need to eat.

00:54:23.602 --> 00:54:24.770 line:80%
How about a sandwich?

00:54:25.270 --> 00:54:27.189 line:20%
SUBWAY

00:54:29.608 --> 00:54:30.609 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:30.692 --> 00:54:31.735 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:54:32.944 --> 00:54:35.197 line:80%
I see you really like sandwiches.

00:54:35.280 --> 00:54:36.281 line:80%
[both chuckle]

00:54:36.990 --> 00:54:37.991 line:80%
Not exactly.

00:54:38.825 --> 00:54:42.204 line:80%
I was so preoccupied earlier
that I didn't get a chance to eat.

00:54:42.287 --> 00:54:44.581 line:80%
And this is really good.

00:54:44.664 --> 00:54:45.791 line:80%
Eat up.

00:54:45.874 --> 00:54:48.001 line:80%
I order this all the time
when I'm working late.

00:54:52.297 --> 00:54:53.548 line:80%
Thank you.

00:54:53.632 --> 00:54:55.759 line:80%
He was just
on the verge of collapse earlier.

00:54:55.842 --> 00:54:58.053 line:80%
My mind went blank.

00:54:58.887 --> 00:55:00.597 line:80%
You were a huge help.

00:55:00.680 --> 00:55:02.182 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:55:04.309 --> 00:55:06.478 line:80%
But wouldn't he be better off
returning to the palace?

00:55:06.561 --> 00:55:08.105 line:80%
There are physicians at the palace.

00:55:08.188 --> 00:55:11.483 line:80%
I'm sure that will be more comfortable
than staying in some hotel room.

00:55:16.988 --> 00:55:19.199 line:80%
He despises being the center of attention.

00:55:19.908 --> 00:55:21.618 line:80%
The physicians would freak out
if they knew.

00:55:21.701 --> 00:55:24.329 line:80%
The Royal Medical Institution
would be on standby all day.

00:55:24.830 --> 00:55:27.791 line:80%
The Royal Kitchen would be cooking
all sorts of soups and porridges.

00:55:27.874 --> 00:55:30.836 line:80%
Royal Seoul Hospital would be the same.
It'd be worse if anything.

00:55:30.919 --> 00:55:32.045 line:80%
As soon as he steps inside,

00:55:32.129 --> 00:55:35.757 line:80%
photos will be taken,
and all kinds of rumors will spread.

00:55:36.716 --> 00:55:37.717 line:80%
Hmm…

00:55:38.218 --> 00:55:39.386 line:80%
[phone buzzes]

00:55:45.142 --> 00:55:46.143 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:55:47.394 --> 00:55:48.520 line:80%
-You need to go.
-What?

00:55:48.603 --> 00:55:51.148 line:80%
The Queen Mother is here.

00:55:51.231 --> 00:55:53.150 line:80%
-Get up.
-Who? Mother?

00:55:53.233 --> 00:55:55.569 line:80%
You need to get out of here.
The Queen Mother…

00:55:55.652 --> 00:55:57.821 line:80%
-Where can I hide you? Come on.
-What's going on?

00:55:57.904 --> 00:56:00.782 line:80%
-Where are you taking me?
-You have to be quiet.

00:56:05.495 --> 00:56:08.415 line:80%
You can do this. You got this, Choi Hyeon.

00:56:12.836 --> 00:56:15.672 line:80%
-Your Majesty, what brings you by?
-Step aside.

00:56:16.548 --> 00:56:18.091 line:80%
It is already quite late. Tomorrow…

00:56:21.511 --> 00:56:22.512 line:80%
[sighs]

00:56:36.568 --> 00:56:38.570 line:80%
[♪ intense music plays]

00:56:49.581 --> 00:56:51.333 line:80%
Tell her I am not yet suitably attired

00:56:53.043 --> 00:56:54.252 line:80%
and that she must wait.

00:57:18.068 --> 00:57:20.278 line:80%
[breathes shakily, sighs]

00:57:29.162 --> 00:57:30.705 line:80%
[sighs]

00:57:48.056 --> 00:57:50.308 line:80%
When the day breaks,
get yourself suitably attired

00:57:50.392 --> 00:57:52.060 line:80%
to answer for today's transgression.

00:57:55.188 --> 00:57:56.731 line:80%
That is what you will tell him.

00:58:04.155 --> 00:58:05.365 line:80%
What now?

00:58:13.832 --> 00:58:15.875 line:80%
[phone ringing]

00:58:15.959 --> 00:58:18.420 line:80%
[groans]

00:58:27.053 --> 00:58:29.222 line:80%
-Yeah?
-[Ms. Do] <i>Ms. Seong, where are you?</i>

00:58:29.306 --> 00:58:32.684 line:80%
Ms. Do, do you know
what time it is right now?

00:58:32.767 --> 00:58:33.935 line:80%
<i>Where are you?</i>

00:58:34.978 --> 00:58:36.229 line:80%
At the hotel.

00:58:36.313 --> 00:58:38.481 line:80%
-<i>Stay right there.</i>
-What?

00:58:38.565 --> 00:58:40.608 line:80%
<i>Stay in your room. I'll come to you.</i>

00:58:40.692 --> 00:58:41.693 line:80%
<i>Got it?</i>

00:58:42.319 --> 00:58:43.445 line:80%
[sighs]

00:58:43.528 --> 00:58:44.529 line:80%
[line disconnects]

00:58:45.280 --> 00:58:46.781 line:80%
What's wrong with her?

00:58:49.617 --> 00:58:51.453 line:80%
[sighs]

00:58:51.536 --> 00:58:53.371 line:80%
PRINCE I-AN SPOTTED
IN SECRET TRYST

00:58:53.455 --> 00:58:54.873 line:80%
WITH CASTLE BEAUTY SEONG HUIJU

00:58:54.956 --> 00:58:57.500 line:80%
[indistinct chattering]

00:58:57.584 --> 00:58:59.544 line:80%
WHERE THE ROYAL COUPLE
ENJOYS THEIR TIME OFF…

00:59:00.920 --> 00:59:02.130 line:80%
…A SECRET DATE AT A HOTEL…

00:59:02.213 --> 00:59:03.214 line:80%
ROYAL PAIR ROCKS…

00:59:03.298 --> 00:59:05.133 line:80%
PRINCE I-AN'S SECRET LOVER…

00:59:06.343 --> 00:59:07.844 line:80%
[phone ringing]

00:59:07.927 --> 00:59:09.679 line:80%
-No, no.
-[employee] Yes, Reporter Kim.

00:59:09.763 --> 00:59:12.515 line:80%
-I'll get back to you.
-No, we haven't confirmed anything yet.

00:59:12.599 --> 00:59:14.601 line:80%
-Yes, will do.
-No, not at all.

00:59:14.684 --> 00:59:15.977 line:80%
-Just a moment.
-Hello?

00:59:16.061 --> 00:59:17.228 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:59:17.312 --> 00:59:19.022 line:80%
Is Seong Huiju insane?

00:59:19.105 --> 00:59:20.774 line:80%
-Why? What's up?
-Look at this.

00:59:22.942 --> 00:59:23.985 line:80%
WEDDING BELLS…

00:59:25.862 --> 00:59:27.322 line:80%
[gasps, exclaims]

00:59:27.405 --> 00:59:28.907 line:80%
Oh my goodness! [gasps]

00:59:30.033 --> 00:59:33.286 line:80%
-Do you think they slept together?
-Of course, they were at a hotel!

00:59:33.370 --> 00:59:35.497 line:80%
[chuckles, inhales sharply]

00:59:36.081 --> 00:59:37.540 line:80%
Ooh…

00:59:37.624 --> 00:59:39.376 line:80%
What are you so happy about?

00:59:39.459 --> 00:59:40.794 line:80%
What? Are you jealous of her?

00:59:42.212 --> 00:59:44.047 line:80%
You are unbelievable.

00:59:47.342 --> 00:59:50.637 line:80%
Ah… Is that why
she turned down all those dates?

00:59:52.472 --> 00:59:53.681 line:80%
You think so?

00:59:53.765 --> 00:59:55.850 line:80%
[chuckles, scoffs]

00:59:56.434 --> 00:59:58.937 line:80%
"Grand Prince I-AN's secret lover"?

01:00:00.730 --> 01:00:01.731 line:80%
Me?

01:00:02.857 --> 01:00:04.609 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:00:06.569 --> 01:00:10.073 line:80%
Pull yourself together, Do Hyejeong.
You've been through far worse.

01:00:10.156 --> 01:00:11.533 line:80%
You got this. Damn it.

01:00:11.616 --> 01:00:13.535 line:80%
Calm down.

01:00:13.618 --> 01:00:14.953 line:80%
Who'd believe this crap?

01:00:15.578 --> 01:00:17.539 line:80%
Why wouldn't they?

01:00:17.622 --> 01:00:18.915 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

01:00:18.998 --> 01:00:21.167 line:80%
Look. They have photos.

01:00:22.001 --> 01:00:24.337 line:80%
Prince I-AN checks in at 4:00 p.m. Snap.

01:00:24.421 --> 01:00:27.006 line:80%
You check in at 7:00 p.m. Snap.

01:00:27.090 --> 01:00:28.216 line:80%
You step out at 9:00 p.m.

01:00:28.299 --> 01:00:31.177 line:80%
to return at 9:30 p.m.
with sandwiches. Snap.

01:00:31.261 --> 01:00:34.472 line:80%
And you can even see
where you got the sandwiches from.

01:00:34.556 --> 01:00:36.015 line:80%
-Really?
-Yes.

01:00:36.099 --> 01:00:39.060 line:80%
Wow. That sandwich place
just hit the jackpot.

01:00:39.727 --> 01:00:41.688 line:80%
They should pay us for the PR.

01:00:41.771 --> 01:00:43.273 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-Ms. Seong.

01:00:44.399 --> 01:00:45.525 line:80%
All right. I hear you.

01:00:46.151 --> 01:00:48.278 line:80%
But I swear nothing happened.

01:00:48.862 --> 01:00:51.489 line:80%
We were with Aide Choi and stuff.

01:00:51.573 --> 01:00:52.866 line:80%
Oh, I see.

01:00:52.949 --> 01:00:56.035 line:80%
Who cares about that
when Aide Choi isn't in a single shot?

01:00:56.119 --> 01:00:58.288 line:80%
-Not even a single royal guard.
-[sighs]

01:00:58.371 --> 01:00:59.706 line:80%
What a great narrative.

01:01:00.331 --> 01:01:02.792 line:80%
"Prince I-AN Dismisses
Royal Guards for Secret Tryst."

01:01:02.876 --> 01:01:04.878 line:80%
From the riding grounds

01:01:04.961 --> 01:01:06.546 line:80%
to a traditional restaurant,

01:01:06.629 --> 01:01:08.882 line:80%
all sorts of location shoots for you.

01:01:08.965 --> 01:01:10.758 line:80%
-[phone buzzes]
-[Hyejeong sighs]

01:01:10.842 --> 01:01:12.385 line:80%
SEONGSAN DAILY REPORTER
AN SAEHUN

01:01:15.722 --> 01:01:17.056 line:80%
HAEMYEONG REPORTER JEONG SUJIN

01:01:17.140 --> 01:01:18.475 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:01:21.811 --> 01:01:23.980 line:80%
First of all,
why did you call for your doctor?

01:01:24.856 --> 01:01:25.899 line:80%
They got him too?

01:01:27.150 --> 01:01:29.861 line:80%
Thanks to that shot,
they're even speculating you're pregnant.

01:01:29.944 --> 01:01:31.738 line:80%
What? [scoffs]

01:01:33.114 --> 01:01:34.115 line:80%
Wow…

01:01:34.199 --> 01:01:36.826 line:80%
You have to hand it
to the public's imagination.

01:01:36.910 --> 01:01:38.328 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:01:38.411 --> 01:01:39.746 line:80%
"A premarital pregnancy"?

01:01:40.371 --> 01:01:41.623 line:80%
-Focus!
-[gasps]

01:01:43.082 --> 01:01:44.083 line:80%
Focus.

01:01:44.709 --> 01:01:46.628 line:80%
Are you sure it will be all right?

01:01:47.754 --> 01:01:50.006 line:80%
I fear this may bring
dishonor to the Crown.

01:01:50.507 --> 01:01:52.050 line:80%
I am sure it will.

01:01:53.009 --> 01:01:55.637 line:80%
The royal family's dignity
will be cast to the ground…

01:01:58.181 --> 01:02:01.476 line:80%
and this woman will be laid
upon the chopping block and carved up.

01:02:02.101 --> 01:02:03.102 line:80%
That must be why…

01:02:05.230 --> 01:02:06.689 line:80%
they are denying it.

01:02:12.779 --> 01:02:14.447 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Are you doing this

01:02:14.531 --> 01:02:17.116 line:80%
because you don't know
who Prince I-AN is for the people?

01:02:18.034 --> 01:02:20.537 line:80%
Did you already forget last year
when you dated the leader

01:02:20.620 --> 01:02:23.581 line:80%
of Idol Galaxy or whatever
and got egged when you were caught?

01:02:23.665 --> 01:02:25.250 line:80%
They keyed your car every other day.

01:02:25.333 --> 01:02:28.378 line:80%
You said it was pure torture
dealing with the overzealous fans

01:02:28.461 --> 01:02:30.380 line:80%
who rang your doorbell at dawn
and ran away.

01:02:30.463 --> 01:02:31.839 line:80%
You must remember that.

01:02:32.924 --> 01:02:33.925 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

01:02:34.008 --> 01:02:35.677 line:80%
Prince I-AN isn't an idol star.

01:02:36.427 --> 01:02:38.054 line:80%
He's so much worse.

01:02:38.137 --> 01:02:41.015 line:80%
Idol stars are beloved
by their fandom alone.

01:02:41.099 --> 01:02:43.893 line:80%
Prince I-AN is beloved
by the whole country.

01:02:43.977 --> 01:02:44.978 line:80%
Everyone.

01:02:45.061 --> 01:02:46.437 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:02:46.521 --> 01:02:47.522 line:80%
I don't love him.

01:02:47.605 --> 01:02:48.815 line:80%
-Ms. Seong!
-[gasps]

01:02:50.149 --> 01:02:52.318 line:80%
You're going to scare the baby!

01:02:54.070 --> 01:02:55.405 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:02:55.488 --> 01:02:57.657 line:80%
"A premarital pregnancy"? [chuckles]

01:02:57.740 --> 01:02:58.866 line:80%
Unbelievable.

01:02:59.993 --> 01:03:01.786 line:80%
Right. Got it.

01:03:02.954 --> 01:03:05.957 line:80%
[♪ imposing music plays]

01:03:07.584 --> 01:03:08.960 line:80%
[line ringing]

01:03:14.132 --> 01:03:15.133 line:80%
GRAND PRINCE

01:03:15.216 --> 01:03:16.843 line:80%
SEONG HUIJU

01:03:18.052 --> 01:03:19.429 line:80%
[line ringing]

01:03:20.096 --> 01:03:22.348 line:80%
[automated voice]
<i>The caller is unavailable…</i>

01:03:23.683 --> 01:03:24.684 line:80%
[line disconnects]

01:03:24.767 --> 01:03:26.185 line:80%
Sir.

01:03:26.269 --> 01:03:28.646 line:80%
Still, wouldn't it be best
to contain this quickly?

01:03:28.730 --> 01:03:31.190 line:80%
If people start throwing around
terms like "Royal Risk"…

01:03:31.274 --> 01:03:33.610 line:80%
-It won't be all bad.
-Pardon?

01:03:33.693 --> 01:03:37.155 line:80%
It'll make all the criticism
over the minimum wage freeze disappear.

01:03:37.697 --> 01:03:40.199 line:80%
Leave it for now. It's just a minor fuss.

01:03:40.992 --> 01:03:41.993 line:80%
[secretary 2] Yes, sir.

01:03:53.755 --> 01:03:55.256 line:80%
[Hyeon] To the palace, please.

01:03:56.007 --> 01:03:57.258 line:80%
To my private residence.

01:03:57.342 --> 01:03:58.343 line:80%
[grunts]

01:03:58.426 --> 01:04:00.428 line:80%
You need to make your way
to the palace first.

01:04:00.511 --> 01:04:02.263 line:80%
Prime Minister Min is already there.

01:04:02.347 --> 01:04:04.265 line:80%
The Public Affairs Office
is also looking--

01:04:04.349 --> 01:04:06.142 line:80%
I said, to my private residence.

01:04:08.561 --> 01:04:10.021 line:80%
Have Seong Huiju…

01:04:10.730 --> 01:04:11.898 line:80%
meet me there.

01:04:47.600 --> 01:04:48.685 line:80%
[sighs]

01:04:52.271 --> 01:04:53.606 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:04:58.194 --> 01:05:00.154 line:80%
-This way, Ms. Seong.
-[chuckles]

01:05:21.634 --> 01:05:23.010 line:80%
Am I the only one freaking out?

01:05:23.761 --> 01:05:25.888 line:80%
No. I'm freaking out too.

01:05:33.312 --> 01:05:34.605 line:80%
[Hyeon] Only Ms. Seong may go inside.

01:05:34.689 --> 01:05:37.150 line:80%
His Royal Highness asked
for a private meeting.

01:05:39.819 --> 01:05:42.071 line:80%
I'm fine. Just wait for me here.

01:05:42.155 --> 01:05:43.156 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

01:05:48.119 --> 01:05:49.454 line:80%
[Hyejeong groans]

01:05:56.669 --> 01:05:58.421 line:80%
Is your fever gone?

01:06:00.423 --> 01:06:01.716 line:80%
-As you can see.
-[chuckles]

01:06:03.176 --> 01:06:05.094 line:80%
[chuckles] You're in good spirits.

01:06:05.928 --> 01:06:07.305 line:80%
As you can see.

01:06:07.388 --> 01:06:08.514 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:06:09.557 --> 01:06:11.976 line:80%
I missed you.
Even though I saw you yesterday.

01:06:13.060 --> 01:06:14.103 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:06:20.860 --> 01:06:22.028 line:80%
Let me apologize

01:06:22.987 --> 01:06:24.614 line:80%
for dragging you into this scandal

01:06:24.697 --> 01:06:27.366 line:80%
and letting you become
the scapegoat for it.

01:06:28.201 --> 01:06:29.202 line:80%
All of it.

01:06:31.871 --> 01:06:32.872 line:80%
So?

01:06:34.373 --> 01:06:35.374 line:80%
Tell me what you desire.

01:06:37.543 --> 01:06:38.669 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:06:40.713 --> 01:06:41.714 line:80%
If I tell you,

01:06:43.549 --> 01:06:44.550 line:80%
can you give it to me?

01:06:44.634 --> 01:06:46.052 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:06:46.135 --> 01:06:47.136 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

01:06:47.220 --> 01:06:48.971 line:80%
What I desire

01:06:50.139 --> 01:06:52.141 line:80%
may be terribly difficult to attain.

01:06:57.563 --> 01:06:58.815 line:80%
Let me get this straight.

01:06:58.898 --> 01:07:02.819 line:80%
That woman and His Royal Highness
are actually an item?

01:07:02.902 --> 01:07:06.447 line:80%
Didn't they seem like they had
nothing going on last time she visited?

01:07:06.531 --> 01:07:08.866 line:80%
A secret rendezvous at a hotel?
That's a done deal.

01:07:08.950 --> 01:07:10.785 line:80%
Still, don't you think it's a bit weird?

01:07:10.868 --> 01:07:12.745 line:80%
His Royal Highness is so busy.

01:07:12.829 --> 01:07:14.622 line:80%
When did he have time to date?

01:07:14.705 --> 01:07:15.748 line:80%
Areum.

01:07:16.374 --> 01:07:18.000 line:80%
I've told you a hundred times.

01:07:18.709 --> 01:07:21.254 line:80%
When people say they can't date
because they're too busy,

01:07:22.088 --> 01:07:23.756 line:80%
it's just an excuse.

01:07:37.645 --> 01:07:38.646 line:80%
Do you remember?

01:07:40.815 --> 01:07:42.066 line:80%
It's a Flower of Honor.

01:07:42.650 --> 01:07:44.318 line:80%
The one I received after I beat you.

01:07:47.405 --> 01:07:49.115 line:80%
[cheering]

01:08:02.587 --> 01:08:03.838 line:80%
[scorekeeper] Seven points!

01:08:03.921 --> 01:08:05.923 line:80%
[cheering]

01:08:18.519 --> 01:08:20.187 line:80%
CHEONGNYONG: 109 POINTS

01:08:21.105 --> 01:08:22.315 line:80%
[sighs]

01:08:31.782 --> 01:08:32.867 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:08:32.950 --> 01:08:34.201 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Didn't feel like crap?</i>

01:08:37.246 --> 01:08:38.915 line:80%
It felt like crap to me.

01:08:40.875 --> 01:08:43.002 line:80%
Losing to someone

01:08:44.211 --> 01:08:45.254 line:80%
who I could have beaten.

01:08:49.508 --> 01:08:50.509 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:08:51.385 --> 01:08:53.095 line:80%
My brother is an idiot.

01:08:54.180 --> 01:08:57.099 line:80%
He got kicked out of the school
we made a donation to.

01:08:57.183 --> 01:09:00.353 line:80%
He even managed to tank a business
that would've run on its own.

01:09:03.356 --> 01:09:05.149 line:80%
But my father and the board

01:09:06.067 --> 01:09:08.778 line:80%
are always dying to replace me with him

01:09:09.403 --> 01:09:11.822 line:80%
whenever I make the slightest mistake.

01:09:13.074 --> 01:09:14.742 line:80%
As if they've been biding their time.

01:09:15.993 --> 01:09:17.370 line:80%
Why do you think that is?

01:09:18.871 --> 01:09:20.539 line:80%
Because he was born before me?

01:09:20.623 --> 01:09:22.875 line:80%
Because he's a son? And a legitimate heir?

01:09:25.836 --> 01:09:26.837 line:80%
Oh…

01:09:28.214 --> 01:09:30.341 line:80%
Perhaps it's because he married
into a noble family.

01:09:32.426 --> 01:09:33.678 line:80%
That's why…

01:09:37.431 --> 01:09:39.225 line:80%
I'm looking to marry up.

01:09:39.809 --> 01:09:40.977 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:09:43.562 --> 01:09:45.356 line:80%
You would marry me for nothing more

01:09:46.524 --> 01:09:47.733 line:80%
than a hollow title?

01:09:47.817 --> 01:09:51.737 line:80%
Because I've lost countless opportunities
simply for not having that title.

01:09:53.823 --> 01:09:56.367 line:80%
[♪ soft music plays]

01:10:06.794 --> 01:10:09.714 line:80%
Prepare yourself to become
the Grand Prince's wife.

01:10:18.014 --> 01:10:19.098 line:80%
You will be up against…

01:10:20.891 --> 01:10:21.892 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:10:22.601 --> 01:10:24.520 line:80%
…the whole nation.

01:10:25.730 --> 01:10:27.732 line:80%
[♪ music intensifies]

01:10:30.818 --> 01:10:31.819 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:10:37.867 --> 01:10:39.035 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:10:45.041 --> 01:10:47.960 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:11:24.080 --> 01:11:27.792 line:80%
[journalist] <i>Your Royal Highness,</i>
<i>is your scandal with CEO Seong Huiju true?</i>

01:11:27.875 --> 01:11:31.087 line:80%
The top five trending key words
are all about you.

01:11:31.170 --> 01:11:32.630 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>He's even a good actor.</i>

01:11:32.713 --> 01:11:34.548 line:80%
You're really going to marry him?

01:11:34.632 --> 01:11:36.801 line:80%
I have to marry him right now.

01:11:36.884 --> 01:11:38.886 line:80%
[student] <i>Stay away</i>
<i>from His Royal Highness!</i>

01:11:38.969 --> 01:11:40.930 line:80%
She will be staying here
for the time being.

01:11:41.013 --> 01:11:42.973 line:20%
[Yun] <i>An investigation is required.</i>

01:11:43.057 --> 01:11:45.851 line:20%
[official] <i>Cooperate with the Junghwajeon</i>
<i>Hall fire investigation, please.</i>

01:11:45.935 --> 01:11:47.311 line:20%
<i>It's fine.</i>

01:11:47.394 --> 01:11:49.897 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>I'm used to going up</i>
<i>against people like that.</i>

01:11:49.980 --> 01:11:52.316 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>I must appear</i>
<i>insanely infatuated with you</i>

01:11:53.609 --> 01:11:55.027 line:20%
for people to believe

01:11:56.153 --> 01:11:57.988 line:20%
<i>this absurd marriage is genuine.</i>

01:12:12.253 --> 01:12:13.879 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:12:13.963 --> 01:12:15.965 line:80%
Translated by Justin S. Kim